name: Dahlia
description:
Dahlia is slowly and clumsily. She worked as a nanny for a while. Everyone love her because she is a lovely and kind.

Her special skill is the use of medicinal herbs. The villagers would come to her for herbs when they were unwell.

Lavender is Her flower. It is a deep blue-purple shade in color. composed of multiple, small purple flowers. It is represent healing and calmness.

If you want to meet her. Dahlia was often at the flower garden outside the village to collect herbs and flowers.
